  "name": "Nagaraja COU1 — Non-cannulated pedicle screw compression-bending credibility assessment (Minimal Profile)",
  "description": "V&V 40 credibility assessment for FEA prediction of ASTM F1717 static compression-bending performance of a non-cannulated 7.5 mm pedicle screw construct. The FEA model ensemble (FDA, Ansys, DePuy Synthes) is compared against N=11 experimental constructs across two laboratories. All 13 V&V 40 factors assessed; one factor (Test conditions) below required level due to single test condition. Intended use is limited to static compression-bending loading of non-cannulated posterior spinal fixation constructs in the context of 510(k) substantial equivalence demonstration. Assurance level: Medium; device class: Class II; model risk level: 3.",
  "bindsRequirement": "https://uofa.net/synth/req/nagaraja-f1717-compression-bending-req-001",
  "bindsClaim": "https://uofa.net/synth/claim/nagaraja-fea-f1717-static-cbending-claim-001",
  "bindsModel": "https://uofa.net/synth/model/nagaraja-fea-pedicle-screw-ensemble-v1",
